    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Spring-Framework-개발환경-설정"><a href="#Spring-Framework-개발환경-설정" class="headerlink" title="Spring Framework 개발환경 설정"></a>Spring Framework 개발환경 설정</h1><p><img src="https://spring.io/img/spring-by-pivotal.png" alt=""><span style="
font-size:10px">[이미지 출처: <a href="https://spring.io/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://spring.io/</a>]</span></p>
<h2 id="실습환경"><a href="#실습환경" class="headerlink" title="실습환경"></a>실습환경</h2><ul>
<li>OS: Ubuntu 16.04.2 LTS</li>
<li>JDK: 1.8.0_121</li>
<li>IDE: Eclipse_Neon.3 Release (4.6.3)</li>
</ul>
